  "original_title": "\u0b95\u0bca\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0b9f\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bc8\u0bb0\u0bb8\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf \u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bc1 \u0b95\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0baa\u0bbf\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Discovery of a new strain of the Covid virus",
      "author": "T. Saranya",
      "body_lines": [
        "Chandima Jeewandara, Director, Department of Immunology and Molecular Medicine, University of Sri Jayewardenepura, said that a new strain of the Kovit virus has been identified.",
        "Meanwhile, medical expert Chandima Jeevandara said on her official Twitter page that the new virus has not yet been detected in the country.",
        "Doctor Chandima Jeevandara said the new virus, dubbed BA 5, was being closely tested and the virus had been reported in 63 countries.",
        "He points out that the new virus identified is spreading faster than other viruses and that strains of the previous Kovit 19 virus are spreading more quickly."
      ],
